<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Commands - Joshua Music Bot</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: 'class',
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        spotify: {
                            green: '#1DB954',
                            black: '#191414',
                            dark: '#121212',
                            gray: '#282828',
                            lightgray: '#b3b3b3'
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Circular:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Circular', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        .scrollbar-hide::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .scrollbar-hide {
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-black text-white">
    <div class="flex h-screen overflow-hidden">
        <%- include('partials/sidebar', { activePage: 'commands' }) %>
        
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
            <%- include('partials/topbar') %>
            
            <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto bg-gradient-to-b from-spotify-dark to-black p-8 scrollbar-hide">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black mb-4">Bot Commands</h1>
                    <p class="text-spotify-lightgray text-lg">All available commands - Prefix: <code class="bg-spotify-gray px-3 py-1 rounded">joshua</code></p>
                </div>

                <% commands.forEach((category, idx) => { %>
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4"><%= category.category %></h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <% category.commands.forEach(cmd => { %>
                        <div class="bg-spotify-gray hover:bg-spotify-gray/80 rounded-lg p-5 transition">
                            <div class="mb-2">
                                <code class="text-spotify-green font-semibold"><%= cmd.name %></code>
                                <% if (cmd.alias) { %>
                                    <span class="text-xs text-spotify-lightgray ml-2">or <code class="text-spotify-green"><%= cmd.alias %></code></span>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-spotify-lightgray text-sm"><%= cmd.description %></p>
                        </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <% }); %>

                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-spotify-green to-green-700 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">üí° Quick Tips</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/90">
                        <li>‚óè Bot akan otomatis join voice channel saat kamu pakai <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">joshua play</code></li>
                        <li>‚óè AI autoplay aktif secara default - musik tidak akan berhenti!</li>
                        <li>‚óè Gunakan <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">joshua help</code> di Discord untuk melihat command</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </main>

            <%- include('partials/player') %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/dashboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
